bug.author: brollb
bug.summary: aws-s3-sdk requirejs path is overwritten on new webgme component
bug.description: The aws-s3-sdk requirejs path was added to the incorrect file (config/config.webgme.js) rather than config/config.base.js. This should be updated as the current version will be overwritten on the creation of a new plugin, visualizer, router, etc.
